Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:22.38,op_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}倾泻的雨仿佛眼泪的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.40,op_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}看看我
